After cookie-cutting:
1) add 'extra/jjb-nse' content to 'infra/jjb-nse' repo:
   https://bbpcode.epfl.ch/browse/code/infra%2Fjenkins%2Fjjb-nse/

2) complete Spack recipe in 'extra/spack'; and add it to BlueBrain Spack repo:
   https://github.com/BlueBrain/spack#the-bluebrain-spack-deployment

3) 'extra' folder can now be removed
